    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The way this was all originally planned was that helicopters were not tied to a base, and stayed in the field until they needed to return to reload, and planes stayed in base (possibly limiting the number of planes to the number of airfields, like ra2) unless they were explicitly attacking something.\r\n\r\nOver time people have \"helicopterized\" planes in a haphazard and unplanned way, causing inconsistencies like the ones noted."
  },
  {
