    "body": "I am not sure how to proceed here. You're right, when I attack, they don't return now but instead fly in circle - is it bad? at least consistent with helis and it isn't illogical.\r\nFor me, S for stop is useful (you can achieve it anyway with move to stop somewhere). We could add explicit RTB order after attacking to keep current behaviour.\r\nI guess best is to close this PR (and ignore all Aircraft issues by me for now)."
